    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆Game Overview</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a rice serving game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can serve as much rice as you like. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also serve red rice sometimes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆System</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serve the rice making sure the bowl is facing the right way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆How to Play</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Game Controller</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Button / Down Button: Serve</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left Button / Right Button: Pass</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B Button / Up Button: Flip the bowl</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Keyboard &amp; Mouse</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >C / S / Down Arrow / Space / Left Click: Serve</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >X / A / D / Left Arrow / Right Arrow / Right Click: Pass</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Z / W / Up Arrow / Mouse Wheel: Flip the bowl</p>",
